This directory is used for the point data, such as airfields, navaids, ...

KFLog supports two different point data sources:

 1. WELT2000. The latest file is to find here:

    http://www.segelflug.de/vereine/welt2000/download/WELT2000.TXT

    More information about WELT2000 is available at:

    http://www.segelflug.de/vereine/welt2000/

 2. openAIP point data from http://www.openaip.net/. See there
    for more information.

KFLog downloads point data files automatically for you in the settings
airfields page. Please define on that page, which point data source
(Welt2000 or openAIP) do you want to use and for which countries point
data should be loaded.
